Package ddf.catalog.data.impl

Provides the classes for the Catalog Data API reference implementation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeDescriptorImpl
    Simple implementation of AttributeDescriptor
    AttributeImpl
    A simple implementation of Attribute.
    AttributeRegistryImpl  
    BasicTypes
    Constants for basic types, both MetacardType and AttributeType
    BinaryContentImpl
    This class is a common implementation of the BinaryContent interface.
    ContentTypeImpl
    This class is a common implementation of the ContentType interface.
    MetacardImpl
    Implements the Metacard's required attributes.
    MetacardTypeImpl
    Default implementation of the MetacardType, used by BasicTypes to create the BasicTypes.BASIC_METACARD.
    QualifiedMetacardTypeImpl
    Default implementation of the QualifiedMetacardType.
    ResultImpl
    Default implementation of the Result interface, which is a Metacard catalog entry wrapped with the extra attributes relevanceScore and distanceInMeters.

Package ddf.catalog.data.impl Description

Provides the classes for the Catalog Data API reference implementation.
